.TH DRIB 1 LOCAL
.SH NAME
drib - open source packaging and distribution script built for web developers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B drib [options]
.I sub-command [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION 
drib allows you to distribute (install) your code more effectively by providing a packaging and central distribution repository.
.SH OPTIONS

.IP "help - display help documentation"
.IP "self-install - install drib"
.TP 10
 --type
.TP 
type of package to create
.IP "install - install a package"
.IP "create - create a package"
.IP "remove - remove a package"
.IP "set - set a package variable"
.IP "unset - unset a package variable"
.IP "list - list installed packages"

.SH AUTHOR
Travis Kuhl (c) 2010